Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\bord0\c&HAF9E86&\pos(893,656)}#狸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs19\bord0\c&HA4A4A5&\pos(593,673)}赞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs19\bord0\c&HA4A4A5&\pos(593,697)}评论
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我发现自己都高二了还一件都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,初中的时候你也什么都没做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:03:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,才觉得高中三年一定得做点什么才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得浑浑噩噩过日子不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\frz270\fs30\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(1252,34)}青春是等不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\frz270\fs30\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(1210,34)}勇气 干劲 活力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\frz270\fs30\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(1168,34)}你能行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\frz270\fs30\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(1126,34)}布丁是饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\frz270\fs30\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(1082,34)}想要保护你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\frz270\fs30\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(1040,34)}不前进就不会开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\frz270\fs30\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(996,34)}珍惜现在这个瞬间
Comment: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\frz270\fs30\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(954,34)}留下遗憾和后悔的高中生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,时间明明就很有限
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时的决心到底哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你准备做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\c&H42433A&\pos(250,404)\frz32.31\fad(500,0)}挥洒青春。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我想实行一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\c&HCEDCC7&\pos(106,126)}1.表示建议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\c&HCEDCC7&\pos(564,564)}（去～怎么样）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,东京？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 先去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然后踏上没有目的的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,随心所向 浪迹天涯！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,enjoy your trip
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我要逃 逃学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,唔 也没什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我要请假啊 装病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说 这点事没什么关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这点事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,难不成你没装病请过假？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,小惠你有过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊 谁都会有过一两次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,崇拜你！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,别那么看我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那那 没有目的的旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那就没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那那那…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不跟你去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我想问什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你会想的事情 用脚趾头都能猜到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那种事就是要一个人去才有意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,想去就去呗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我会帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,明天要在车站的洗手间换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 是大海 大海耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕 群马腔会被认出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这就要走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么背这么大个包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 没什么 我跟朋友借了体操服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,别给我打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可是嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心 我已经帮你跟学校请过假了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,用这种声音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要在外面过夜 我会跟你统一口径的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你就放心去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在洗手间换好衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,坐上和学校相反方向的电车
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人跳出平时的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,踏上没有目的的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,去往从未见过的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么会在这？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 今天下雨嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说 还是觉得装病请假不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你没地方想去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊 有好多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,京都 冲绳 北海道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那怎么没去？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,飞机可能会掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,新干线可能会爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,还有可能天上砸陨石？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我向来这样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,参加社团活动的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,学东西的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,想考好学校的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一到关键时刻我就发怵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,担心从来没做过的事要是没做好怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕失败
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得自己可能会后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,每次临到头来我就退缩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛 我觉得也不算坏事就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 我不喜欢这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\fs30\c&H232C28&\frz344.8\pos(602,274)}门禁之前我会回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\fs30\c&H232C28&\frz344.8\pos(72,398)}家常蛋包饭做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我最讨厌自己这一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,下次出去玩吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 你掉东西了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我数了一下 整整一百万
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,一百万？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛带来啊 应该交公吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我当时很慌…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,话怎么说都行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦 是真的 我真的很慌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 掉钱的人好像穿着我们学校的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,高几？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:10:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是扫到了一眼她的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好像…没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她的头发跟那边的女生差不多长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,估计是个美女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还有呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 身上挺香的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是护发素？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 头发那么长的女生应该也没几个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我去高一教室看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好紧张…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这股味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一百万…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,一百万…元…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一百万…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,元！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\frz270\fs30\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(1060,210)\fad(300,0)}开关门{\3c&H32E8EB&}请轻声!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（Partb）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,啊不 其实昨天…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 别误会 我不是偷的 只是碰巧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,南极？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnSimHei\pos(760,130)\frz348.2\fs35}比宇宙更遥远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这本书是我妈妈写的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她原来是个南极考察队队员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不过在我初中的时候失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,然后一直没被找到 也几乎没留下什么遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我要去找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,去南极？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,去得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶 朋友 老师 前辈和邻居都说
